article.headline: Lipscomb 66, Fla Atlantic 50
article.story: BOCA RATON, Fla. (AP) -- Brian Fisk led Lipscomb with 22 points in its 66-50 win over Florida Atlantic Tuesday. James Poindexter followed close behind Fisk with another 20 points for Lipscomb (12-6, 8-2). High scorers for Florida Atlantic (9-8, 8-2) were DeAndre Rice with 17 points and Rodney Webb with 13 points. Lipscomb led Florida Atlantic 34-21 at halftime and held onto its lead during the second half, outscoring Florida Atlantic 32-29. Lipscomb shot 54 percent (13-24) from the floor during the first half while Florida Atlantic shot 40 percent (8-20). Lipscomb shot 50 percent (10-20) during the second half and Florida Atlantic shot 28 percent (9-32).
